Reference

Main function: P-model implementation.

An implementation of the P-model (Prentice et al., 2014; Wang et al., 2017; Stocker et al., 2019) for predicting acclimated photosynthetic parameters, assimilation, and dark respiration rates as a function of the environment.

rpmodel()

Invokes a P-model function call

Public functions used inside `rpmodel()`

Public functions used inside rpmodel(). Made public for documentation, visibility, and other applications by the user.
